    "long_instructions": "## Plan Your Lunches\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you plan your lunches for the week. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Start by entering a **generic prompt** and read AI Chat's response. For example: \r\n\r\n>Help me plan my lunches for the week.\r\n2. Revise your prompt and add specific examples, like **what foods you typically eat** or **which foods you hate**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's updated response.\r\n2. Finally, re-submit your previous prompt and include an **uploaded image**.\r\n3. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**",
